AUDIO: 'Tasks can come from external systems like Linear and Jira, or you can just write them inline during creation. &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; When creating a task, Human Layer manages a multi-repo workspace with work [music] trees for each repo involved.'

[00:31] [scene:talk]
